instruction: Create a shopping list for a 4-person birthday party.
output:
The shopping list should include: 
· Balloons
· Gift wrapping paper 
· Candles 
· Celebration cards 
· Baking ingredients (flour, sugar, butter, eggs)
· Cake decoration supplies 
· Ice cream 
· Snacks (nuts, popcorn, pretzels, chips) 
· Soft drinks 
· Pinata 
· Platters 
· Plates, cups, cutlery 
· Table cloths 
· Goody bags 
· Party favors 
· 4 birthday presents 
· 4 birthday cards.
